         +-----------------------------------+
         |           Pipe Station (ch)       |   <-- Channel (shared message tube)
         |  (1 tunnel, shared by everyone)   |
         +-----------------------------------+
                      ^
                      |
   +------------------+------------------+------------------+
   |                  |                  |                  |
Goroutine #1     Goroutine #2      Goroutine #3      Goroutine #4
   sends             sends             sends             sends
  "Hi"              "from"            "Go"              "Lang"
   |                  |                  |                  |
   +--------------------------------------------------------+
                      |
                 [ Channel ch ]  <-- messages flow here
                      |
                  Main function
                  receives msgs
                      |
               +----------------+
               | Print or Use   |
               | the messages   |
               +----------------+


